    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "What Are Mnemonics?"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "In the world of <a href=\"https://coinmarketcap.com/alexandria/glossary/cryptocurrency\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">cryptocurrencies</a>, mnemonics is a group of words, usually 12 or more that are generated when a new crypto <a href=\"https://coinmarketcap.com/alexandria/glossary/wallet\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wallet </a>is created."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "html": "Mnemonics is 12 words that create private and public key and assign a address."
    },
